[{"text": "I woke up in the middle of the night", "start": 16.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with the sound of heavy explosion.", "start": 18.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It was deep at night.", "start": 21.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I do not remember what time it was.", "start": 23.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I just remember the sound", "start": 25.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was so heavy", "start": 27.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and so very shocking.", "start": 29.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Everything in my room was shaking --", "start": 32.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my heart, my windows,", "start": 35.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my bed, everything.", "start": 38.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I looked out the windows", "start": 42.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I saw a full half-circle", "start": 45.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of explosion.", "start": 48.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I thought it was just like the movies,", "start": 50.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but the movies had not conveyed them", "start": 52.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the powerful image that I was seeing", "start": 54.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "full of bright red", "start": 57.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and orange and gray,", "start": 59.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and a full circle of explosion.", "start": 61.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And I kept on staring at it", "start": 63.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "until it disappeared.", "start": 66.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I went back to my bed,", "start": 69.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I prayed,", "start": 72.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I secretly thanked God", "start": 74.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that that missile", "start": 77.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "did not land on my family's home,", "start": 79.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that it did not kill my family that night.", "start": 83.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thirty years have passed,", "start": 88.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I still feel guilty about that prayer,", "start": 90.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "for the next day, I learned that that missile", "start": 94.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "landed on my brother's friend's home", "start": 96.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and killed him", "start": 100.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and his father,", "start": 103.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "but did not kill his mother or his sister.", "start": 105.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "His mother showed up the next week", "start": 111.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "at my brother's classroom", "start": 113.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and begged seven-year-old kids", "start": 115.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to share with her any picture they may have", "start": 118.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of her son,", "start": 121.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for she had lost everything.", "start": 123.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is not a story", "start": 129.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of a nameless survivor of war,", "start": 131.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and nameless refugees,", "start": 135.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "whose stereotypical images we see in our newspapers", "start": 137.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and our TV", "start": 140.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with tattered clothes,", "start": 143.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "dirty face, scared eyes.", "start": 145.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "This is not a story of a nameless someone", "start": 149.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who lived in some war,", "start": 152.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who we do not know their hopes, their dreams,", "start": 154.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "their accomplishments, their families,", "start": 156.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "their beliefs, their values.", "start": 159.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is my story.", "start": 161.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was that girl.", "start": 165.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I am another image and vision", "start": 169.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of another survivor of war.", "start": 172.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I am that refugee,", "start": 175.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I am that girl.", "start": 177.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You see,", "start": 180.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I grew up in war-torn Iraq,", "start": 182.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I believe that there are two sides of wars", "start": 186.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and we've only seen", "start": 189.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "one side of it.", "start": 191.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We only talk about", "start": 193.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "one side of it.", "start": 195.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But there's another side", "start": 197.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that I have witnessed", "start": 199.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as someone who lived in it", "start": 201.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and someone who ended up working in it.", "start": 203.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I grew up with the colors of war --", "start": 206.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the red colors of fire and blood,", "start": 209.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the brown tones of earth", "start": 212.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as it explodes", "start": 215.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in our faces", "start": 217.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the piercing silver", "start": 219.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of an exploded missile,", "start": 221.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so bright", "start": 223.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that nothing can protect your eyes from it.", "start": 225.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I grew up", "start": 229.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with the sounds of war --", "start": 231.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the staccato sounds of gunfire,", "start": 233.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the wrenching booms of explosions,", "start": 236.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "ominous drones of jets flying overhead", "start": 239.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the wailing warning sounds", "start": 242.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of sirens.", "start": 244.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "These are the sounds you would expect,", "start": 247.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but they are also the sounds", "start": 250.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of dissonant concerts of a flock of birds", "start": 252.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "screeching in the night,", "start": 255.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the high-pitched honest cries", "start": 257.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of children", "start": 259.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the thunderous,", "start": 261.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "unbearable", "start": 263.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "silence.", "start": 265.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"War,\" a friend of mine said,", "start": 268.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"is not about sound at all.", "start": 270.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "It is actually about silence,", "start": 273.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the silence of humanity.\"", "start": 276.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I have since left Iraq", "start": 281.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and founded a group called Women for Women International", "start": 284.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that ends up working", "start": 287.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "with women survivors of wars.", "start": 289.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "In my travels and in my work,", "start": 292.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from Congo to Afghanistan,", "start": 294.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "from Sudan to Rwanda,", "start": 297.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I have learned not only", "start": 299.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the colors and the sounds of war are the same,", "start": 301.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but the fears of war are the same.", "start": 304.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "You know, there is a fear of dying,", "start": 308.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and do not believe any movie character", "start": 310.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where the hero is not afraid.", "start": 313.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It is very scary", "start": 315.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to go through that feeling", "start": 317.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of \"I am about to die\"", "start": 319.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or \"I could die in this explosion.\"", "start": 321.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But there's also the fear", "start": 324.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of losing loved ones,", "start": 326.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I think that's even worse.", "start": 328.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's too painful. You don't want to think about it.", "start": 330.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "But I think the worst kind of fear is the fear --", "start": 333.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "as Samia, a Bosnian woman, once told me,", "start": 337.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who survived the four-years besiege of Sarajevo;", "start": 340.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "she said, \"The fear", "start": 343.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of losing", "start": 345.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the 'I' in me,", "start": 347.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the fear of losing", "start": 349.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the 'I' in me.\"", "start": 352.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "That's what my mother in Iraq", "start": 354.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "used to tell me.", "start": 356.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It's like dying from inside-out.", "start": 358.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A Palestinian woman once told me,", "start": 362.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"It is not about the fear of one death,\"", "start": 364.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "she said, \"sometimes I feel", "start": 367.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I die 10 times in one day,\"", "start": 369.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as she was describing the marches of soldiers", "start": 372.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the sounds of their bullets.", "start": 374.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "She said, \"But it's not fair,", "start": 376.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because there is only one life,", "start": 378.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and there should only be one death.\"", "start": 381.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We have been only seeing", "start": 387.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "one side of war.", "start": 390.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We have only been discussing and consumed", "start": 392.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with high-level preoccupations", "start": 395.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "over troop levels, drawdown timelines,", "start": 397.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "surges and sting operations,", "start": 400.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "when we should be examining the details", "start": 402.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of where the social fabric", "start": 405.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "has been most torn,", "start": 408.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where the community has improvised", "start": 411.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and survived", "start": 413.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and shown acts of resilience", "start": 415.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and amazing courage", "start": 417.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "just to keep life going.", "start": 419.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We have been so consumed", "start": 423.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with seemingly objective discussions", "start": 426.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of politics, tactics,", "start": 428.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "weapons, dollars", "start": 430.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and casualties.", "start": 432.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is the language", "start": 434.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of sterility.", "start": 436.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "How casually", "start": 439.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we treat casualties", "start": 441.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the context of this topic.", "start": 443.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "This is where we conceive of rape and casualties", "start": 445.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "as inevitabilities.", "start": 448.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Eighty percent of refugees around the world", "start": 451.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are women and children. Oh.", "start": 454.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Ninety percent of modern war casualties", "start": 457.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are civilians.", "start": 459.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Seventy-five percent of them are women and children.", "start": 461.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "How interesting.", "start": 464.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Oh, half a million women in Rwanda", "start": 467.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "get raped in 100 days.", "start": 469.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Or, as we speak now,", "start": 471.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "hundreds of thousands of Congolese women", "start": 474.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are getting raped and mutilated.", "start": 477.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "How interesting.", "start": 479.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "These just become numbers that we refer to.", "start": 481.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "The front of wars", "start": 485.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "is increasingly non-human eyes", "start": 487.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "peering down on our perceived enemies", "start": 490.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from space,", "start": 492.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "guiding missiles toward unseen targets,", "start": 494.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "while the human conduct", "start": 497.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the orchestra of media relations", "start": 499.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the event that this particular drone attack", "start": 501.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "hits a villager", "start": 504.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "instead of an extremist.", "start": 506.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "It is a chess game.", "start": 508.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You learn to play an international relations school", "start": 510.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "on your way out and up", "start": 513.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to national and international leadership.", "start": 515.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Checkmate.", "start": 518.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We are missing", "start": 521.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a completely other side of wars.", "start": 523.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We are missing my mother's story,", "start": 527.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who made sure with every siren, with every raid,", "start": 530.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with every cut off-of electricity,", "start": 533.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "she played puppet shows for my brothers and I,", "start": 535.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "so we would not be scared", "start": 537.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the sounds of explosions.", "start": 539.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We are missing the story of Fareeda,", "start": 541.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a music teacher,", "start": 544.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "a piano teacher, in Sarajevo,", "start": 546.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who made sure", "start": 548.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that she kept the music school open", "start": 550.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "every single day", "start": 552.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the four years of besiege in Sarajevo", "start": 554.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and walked to that school,", "start": 557.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "despite the snipers shooting", "start": 559.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "at that school and at her,", "start": 561.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and kept the piano, the violin, the cello", "start": 563.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "playing the whole duration of the war,", "start": 566.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "with students wearing their gloves and hats and coats.", "start": 569.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "That was her fight.", "start": 572.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "That was her resistance.", "start": 574.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We are missing the story of Nehia,", "start": 577.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a Palestinian woman in Gaza", "start": 580.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who, the minute there was a cease-fire in the last year's war,", "start": 582.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "she left out of home,", "start": 585.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "collected all the flour", "start": 587.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and baked as much bread for every neighbor to have,", "start": 589.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in case there is no cease-fire the day after.", "start": 592.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We are missing", "start": 596.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the stories of Violet,", "start": 598.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who, despite surviving genocide in the church massacre,", "start": 600.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "she kept on going on,", "start": 603.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "burying bodies, cleaning homes, cleaning the streets.", "start": 605.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We are missing stories of women", "start": 608.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "who are literally keeping life going", "start": 611.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in the midst of wars.", "start": 614.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Do you know --", "start": 616.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "do you know that people fall in love in war", "start": 618.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and go to school", "start": 621.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and go to factories and hospitals", "start": 624.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and get divorced and go dancing and go playing", "start": 626.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and live life going?", "start": 628.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And the ones who are keeping that life", "start": 632.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "are women.", "start": 634.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "There are two sides of war.", "start": 637.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is a side that fights,", "start": 641.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and there is a side that keeps the schools", "start": 643.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the factories and the hospitals open.", "start": 645.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is a side that is focused on winning battles,", "start": 648.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and there is a side that is focused", "start": 651.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "on winning life.", "start": 653.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is a side that leads the front-line discussion,", "start": 656.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and there is a side", "start": 659.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that leads the back-line discussion.", "start": 661.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is a side that thinks", "start": 664.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that peace is the end of fighting,", "start": 666.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and there is a side that thinks", "start": 670.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that peace is the arrival", "start": 672.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of schools and jobs.", "start": 674.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is a side", "start": 677.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that is led by men,", "start": 679.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and there is a side", "start": 681.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that is led by women.", "start": 683.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And in order for us to understand", "start": 685.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "how do we build lasting peace,", "start": 688.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "we must understand war and peace", "start": 691.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "from both sides.", "start": 694.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We must have a full picture", "start": 696.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of what that means.", "start": 698.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "In order for us to understand", "start": 700.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "what actually peace means,", "start": 702.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we need to understand,", "start": 704.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as one Sudanese woman once told me,", "start": 706.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Peace is the fact that my toenails", "start": 708.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are growing back again.\"", "start": 711.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "She grew up in Sudan, in Southern Sudan,", "start": 714.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "for 20 years of war,", "start": 716.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "where it killed one million people", "start": 718.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and displaced five million refugees.", "start": 721.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Many women were taken as slaves", "start": 724.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by rebels and soldiers,", "start": 726.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as sexual slaves who were forced also", "start": 728.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to carry the ammunition and the water", "start": 731.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the food for the soldiers.", "start": 733.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So that woman walked for 20 years,", "start": 735.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "so she would not be kidnapped again.", "start": 738.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And only when there was some sort of peace,", "start": 741.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "her toenails grew back again.", "start": 744.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We need to understand peace", "start": 748.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from a toenail's perspective.", "start": 750.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We need to understand", "start": 754.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that we cannot actually have negotiations", "start": 756.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of ending of wars or peace", "start": 758.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "without fully including women", "start": 760.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "at the negotiating table.", "start": 763.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I find it amazing", "start": 765.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that the only group of people", "start": 767.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who are not fighting and not killing", "start": 769.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and not pillaging and not burning and not raping,", "start": 771.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the group of people who are mostly --", "start": 774.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "though not exclusively --", "start": 776.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who are keeping life going in the midst of war,", "start": 778.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are not included in the negotiating table.", "start": 781.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And I do argue that women lead the back-line discussion,", "start": 786.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but there are also men", "start": 789.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who are excluded from that discussion.", "start": 791.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The doctors who are not fighting,", "start": 793.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the artists, the students, the men who refuse to pick up the guns,", "start": 795.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "they are, too, excluded", "start": 798.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "from the negotiating tables.", "start": 800.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is no way we can talk about a lasting peace,", "start": 803.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "building of democracy, sustainable economies,", "start": 806.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "any kind of stabilities,", "start": 809.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if we do not fully include women", "start": 811.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "at the negotiating table.", "start": 814.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Not one, but 50 percent.", "start": 816.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "There is no way we can talk about the building of stability", "start": 820.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "if we don't start investing", "start": 823.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in women and girls.", "start": 826.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Did you know", "start": 828.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that one year", "start": 830.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of the world's military spending", "start": 832.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "equals 700 years", "start": 834.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of the U.N. budget", "start": 837.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and equals 2,928 years", "start": 840.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "of the U.N. budget allocated for women?", "start": 843.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "If we just reverse", "start": 847.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that distribution of funds,", "start": 849.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "perhaps we could have", "start": 851.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a better lasting peace in this world.", "start": 854.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And last, but not least,", "start": 857.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we need to invest in peace and women,", "start": 859.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not only because it is the right thing to do,", "start": 862.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not only because it is the right thing to do,", "start": 865.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "for all of us to build sustainable and lasting peace today,", "start": 868.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but it is for the future.", "start": 871.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "A Congolese woman,", "start": 874.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who was telling me about", "start": 876.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "how her children saw their father killed in front of them", "start": 878.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and saw her raped in front of them", "start": 881.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and mutilated in front of them,", "start": 884.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and her children saw their nine-year-old sibling", "start": 886.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "killed in front of them,", "start": 888.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "how they're doing okay right now.", "start": 891.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "She got into Women for Women International's program.", "start": 894.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "She got a support network.", "start": 896.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "She learned about her rights.", "start": 898.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "We taught her vocational and business skills. We helped her get a job.", "start": 900.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "She was earning 450 dollars. She was doing okay.", "start": 903.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "She was sending them to school. Have a new home.", "start": 906.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "She said, \"But what I worry about the most", "start": 908.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "is not any of that.", "start": 911.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I worry that my children", "start": 913.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "have hate in their hearts,", "start": 915.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and when they want to grow up, they want to fight again", "start": 918.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the killers of their father and their brother.\"", "start": 921.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "We need to invest in women,", "start": 925.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "because that's our only chance", "start": 928.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "to ensure that there is no more war", "start": 931.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the future.", "start": 933.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "That mother has a better chance to heal her children", "start": 935.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "than any peace agreement can do.", "start": 938.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Are there good news? Of course, there are good news. There are lots of good news.", "start": 942.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "To start with, these women that I told you about", "start": 945.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "are dancing and singing every single day,", "start": 948.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and if they can,", "start": 951.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "who are we not to dance?", "start": 953.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "That girl that I told you about", "start": 955.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "ended up starting Women for Women International Group", "start": 957.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that impacted one million people, sent 80 million dollars,", "start": 960.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and I started this from zero,", "start": 963.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "nothing, nada, [unclear].", "start": 965.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 968.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They are women who are standing on their feet", "start": 971.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in spite of their circumstances,", "start": 974.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "not because of it.", "start": 977.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Think of how the world can be a much better place", "start": 980.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "if, for a change,", "start": 983.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have a better equality,", "start": 985.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have equality,", "start": 987.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "we have a representation", "start": 989.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and we understand war,", "start": 991.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "both from the front-line", "start": 993.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and the back-line discussion.", "start": 995.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Rumi, a 13th-century Sufi poet,", "start": 997.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "says, \"Out beyond the worlds", "start": 1000.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "of right-doings and wrong-doings,", "start": 1002.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "there is a field.", "start": 1005.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I will meet you there.", "start": 1007.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "When the soul lies down in that grass,", "start": 1009.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "the world is too full", "start": 1012.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to talk about.", "start": 1014.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Ideas, language,", "start": 1016.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "even the phrase 'each other'", "start": 1018.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "no longer makes any sense.\"", "start": 1020.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I humbly add -- humbly add --", "start": 1024.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that out beyond", "start": 1027.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the worlds of war and peace,", "start": 1029.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "there is a field,", "start": 1032.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and there are many women and men", "start": 1034.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "[who] are meeting there.", "start": 1037.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Let us make this field a much bigger place.", "start": 1040.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Let us all meet in that field.", "start": 1043.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 1046.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 1048.26, "duration": 11.0}]